                     <interp inst="t18130113-29-off163" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130113-29-off163" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               burglarously breaking an entering the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130113-29-victim281" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Beadle
                        <interp inst="t18130113-29-victim281" type="surname" value="Beadle"></interp>
