                  , about the hour of six, in the night of the <rs id="t18130113-29-cd164" type="crimeDate">11th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130113-29-off163 t18130113-29-cd164"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein a key, value 1 s. the property of 
